These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, quad-bike
1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
2. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
3. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the skateboard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | roller | skateboard | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, hiking, puzzles, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | photography | magic-tricks | hiking | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, firefighter, musician, software-developer
1. the firefighter is on the right of the musician##1
2. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
3. the scientist is the scientist##1
4. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the software-developer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | software-developer | scientist | musician | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
