2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | traveling | writing | cooking | rock-climbing |

