3. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | ship | trike | scooter | skateboard |

